<h6>Resume</h6>
<p><a href=\"http://www.linkedin.com/in/balajirsharma\">LinkedIn</a> | <a href=\"mailto:balajirsharma@gmail.com?subject:Hello\">Email</a>  </p>
<h3><strong>Summary</strong></h3>
<hr />
<p>I am currently an engineer at <a href=\"http://www.mathworks.com\">MathWorks</a>, makers of MATLAB, in a customer-facing technical role. I work closely with educators in academia to understand the evolving landscape of STEM education and the role of computational tools therein. My work explores avenues and resources to support pedagogical initiatives and innovations towards enhanced student learning. I have a keen interest, and proficiency, in scientific computing and interactive data visualization. </p>
<p>Read on for a lighter, and hopefully more useful, version of the resume. For a more traditional format, please download a copy below.</p>
